019package com.bewsoftware.utils.struct;
020
021/**
022 * BooleanReturn class provides a way to get a {@code boolean} value into
023 * and out of either a Lambda expression or a method through a parameter.
024 *
025 * @deprecated Replaced with {@link Ref Ref&lt;T&gt;}.
026 *
027 * @author <a href="mailto:bw.opensource@yahoo.com">Bradley Willcott</a>
028 *
029 * @since 1.0.5
030 * @version 1.0.5
031 */
032@Deprecated
033public final class BooleanReturn {
034
035    public boolean val;
036
037    public BooleanReturn() {
038    }
039
040    public BooleanReturn(boolean val) {
041        this.val = val;
042    }
043
044    @Override
045    public String toString() {
046        return "" + val;
047    }
048}
